casebody.head_matter:
State of TEXAS, Plaintiff
v.
State of NEW MEXICO
No. 65, Original
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of the River Master for fees and expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $22,924.06, for the period July 1, 2018, through June 30, 2019, to be paid equally by the parties.
